                            laravel request cycle

  1. user sends a request
  2. request enters index.php this is an entry gate of the laravel
  3. composer autoloads all classes
  4. laravel bootstraps application ( prepares  the framework, it sets up core binding and all configurations)
  5. middleware runs ( middleware binding ,it checks request before it reaches the route like authentication check, or logging etc)
  6. route matching takes place ( laravel matches requested url, view mthod renders, respons to browser)
  7. controller method executes
  8. view renders response
  9. response sent back to browser.


